name: Sic-Six
Lore: 'Gifted engineers. Sic-six believe their technology is superior. Have a poison stinger. Spin vast and intricate webs which create a hazard for landing starships. Avoided by pilots.',
Text: 'Subtracts 2 from forfeit of each opponent''s pilots at same site. Prevents characters from moving to or from same or adjacent sites using Elis Helrot or Nabrun Leids.',
